Welcome Back to Wall Power. I=E2=80=99m Marion Maneker.

=C2=A0

The battle for Artnet ended yesterday in Berlin, not with a bang but with a=
 whimper. There were, however, plenty of fireworks at the company=E2=80=99s=
 long-delayed=E2=80=94since 2023!=E2=80=94annual general meeting. Several s=
hareholders who were there told me it was a wild, 14-hour day. Tonight, I=
=E2=80=99ll take you through what happened and explain why Artnet may now b=
e in play.=C2=A0

=C2=A0

But first=E2=80=A6

* Tyler Mitchell=E2=80=99s street party: Celebrated fashion photographer Ty=
ler Mitchell and Gagosian gallery director Antwaun Sargent have had a perso=
nal and professional relationship for a decade=E2=80=94ever since the latte=
r wrote The New Black Vanguard ( https://www.amazon.com/New-Black-Vanguard-=
Photography-Between/dp/1597114685?utm_campaign=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%=
282%2F28%2F25%29&utm_content=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F27%2F25%29&u=
